In the past year, Lithuania has gone further in countering China by smearing its treatment of Uygurs, undermining the one-China principle and boycotting the Beijing 2022 Winter Olympics among other things. It's being used as a cat's paw of the United States, and Lithuania will pay a big price for that eventually. Credits: Editor: Yuan Xin Designer: Cao Yi Senior producer: Wei Wei Managing director: Mei Yan (To submit cartoons and share story ideas or feedback on our cartoon page, please contact us at cartoon_opinions@cgtn.com)